  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/46db9487e12a7f3c746cc4fdec71122c.avif?t=1734452688\" width=600 height=194 /></span> <br><br>Garden Trills is a cozy puzzle-platforming game following the adventures of a little sparrow through a world of dreamy gardens. Freely reshape the scenery through gardening to reach new destinations! Enjoy up to 10 hours of relaxing exploration, bird quests and flower acrobatics in the whimsical town of Vernubiel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.poster.avif?t=1734452688\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.webm?t=1734452688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.mp4?t=1734452688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself as a little bird exploring a vast world of floating gardens, full of life and vibrant colors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flutter though 100+ open-ended platforming puzzles that will put your gardening creativity to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock 40+ adorable accessories with hundreds of color variants to mix and match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet an adorable cast of bird neighbors you can befriend as you help each other out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely grow beautiful flowers with magical powers to help you in your quest and embellish the town.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/46db9487e12a7f3c746cc4fdec71122c.avif?t=1734452688\" width=600 height=194 /></span> <br><br>Garden Trills is a cozy puzzle-platforming game following the adventures of a little sparrow through a world of dreamy gardens. Freely reshape the scenery through gardening to reach new destinations! Enjoy up to 10 hours of relaxing exploration, bird quests and flower acrobatics in the whimsical town of Vernubiel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.poster.avif?t=1734452688\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.webm?t=1734452688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669500/extras/04c5fd6e78ca87da845c572246978500.mp4?t=1734452688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immerse yourself as a little bird exploring a vast world of floating gardens, full of life and vibrant colors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flutter though 100+ open-ended platforming puzzles that will put your gardening creativity to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock 40+ adorable accessories with hundreds of color variants to mix and match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet an adorable cast of bird neighbors you can befriend as you help each other out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely grow beautiful flowers with magical powers to help you in your quest and embellish the town.</p></li></ul>",
